    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《粪勇前进》是一款高难度的 2D 动作游戏，背景设定在霓虹灯闪耀的世界中，玩家需引导自动前进的“便便”跳跃，将其送至终点马桶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管外观滑稽，但游戏要求玩家具备精确的操控和时机把握。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向所有热爱高难度动作游戏的玩家，献上终极的“技术考验”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101010/extras/9432ab8905eb86eb43794310b302bafc.poster.avif?t=1765858787\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101010/extras/9432ab8905eb86eb43794310b302bafc.webm?t=1765858787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101010/extras/9432ab8905eb86eb43794310b302bafc.mp4?t=1765858787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“本游戏不包含任何感人的故事情节或有魅力的角色元素。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把便便送进马桶吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单却深奥的玩法 </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏操作只有“跳跃”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，仅凭这一个简单的动作，您将需要攻略超过 150 个变化多样的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎接您的将是硬核动作挑战，您需要反复失败，从试错中学习，最终奔向终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富独特的关卡设计</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一触即弹的高跳泡泡、会崩塌的平台、尖刺墙壁、开关（ON/OFF Switches）…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着关卡推进，各种独特的机关将接连出现。要克服每个关卡的陷阱和机关，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您需要瞬间反应能力和解谜般的思考力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>酷炫的视觉和音效 </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古未来主义的霓虹灯光画面，以及令人沉迷的酷炫背景音乐（BGM），共同营造出游戏的时尚氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101010/extras/a527b3bd9e885f1e37528c2cf5b82b20.poster.avif?t=1765858787\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101010/extras/a527b3bd9e885f1e37528c2cf5b82b20.webm?t=1765858787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101010/extras/a527b3bd9e885f1e37528c2cf5b82b20.mp4?t=1765858787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集、扭蛋、定制你的专属便便！ </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消耗在关卡中收集到的“UN-COIN”，可以进行扭蛋以获得便便外观的定制物品，或是解锁更高难度的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含丰富的重玩价值，收集所有独特的物品，以完成收集目标吧。</p>",
